casebody.data:
Primalton H. PETERSON, Appellant,
v.
STATE of Missouri, Respondent. WD 81028 Missouri Court of Appeals, Western District. ORDER FILED: December 18, 2018 S. Kate Webber, Kansas City, MO, for appellant. Nathan J. Aquino, Jefferson City, MO, for respondent. Before Division Three: Gary D. Witt, Presiding Judge, Cynthia L. Martin, Judge and Anthony Rex Gabbert, Judge

ORDER

Per curiam:

Appellant Primalton Peterson ("Peterson") appeals the denial of his Amended Rule 24.035 motion following an evidentiary hearing. Peterson sought to vacate his guilty plea and sentence to second-degree murder pursuant to section 565.021, armed criminal action pursuant to section 571.015, and abandonment of a corpse pursuant to section 194.425. For reasons explained more fully in a memorandum provided to the parties, we affirm. Rule 84.16(b).
